        {
            "title": "收入不到20萬美元免除學費 耶魯這項新政將覆蓋逾八成美國家庭",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 耶魯大學跟進哈佛去年出台的舉措，宣布將為家庭年收入低於20萬美元的本科生免除學費。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該校周二發表聲明稱，強化的助學政策將確保此類家庭的學生「獲得以需求為基礎、足以覆蓋甚至超過學費成本的獎學金」。根據這項將自2026-2027學年起生效的新政，對於來自資產狀況普通且收入不到10萬美元的家庭，學生的所有預期費用都將得以免除。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國歷史最悠久、最富有的高等學府哈佛大學去年宣布免除家庭收入在10萬美元或以下的學生學費及食宿費，而收入不超過20萬美元者可免學費。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f16d9f00-8f34-3a5e-a344-3848dd8ac23a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">學費通常是大學就讀成本中最大的組成部分。除此之外他們的家庭還要負擔食宿費以及交通和洗衣等其它開銷。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「根據這項面向年收入低於20萬美元家庭的新政，超過80%的美國住戶將有資格申請至少可以覆蓋學費成本的耶魯獎學金，」 坐落在康乃迪克州紐黑文的這所名校說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Yale to Offer Free Tuition to Families Making Below $200,000 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B020%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%85%8D%E9%99%A4%E5%AD%B8%E8%B2%BB-%E8%80%B6%E9%AD%AF%E9%80%99%E9%A0%85%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%B0%87%E8%A6%86%E8%93%8B%E9%80%BE%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD-035450983.html",
