        {
            "title": "香港2025年住宅價格錄得四年來首次年度成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Rating and Valuation Department\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7aeRc8MvY9CU7.N8_EHcWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/75e74d8c7be81b995c2e7c6c9ddb372f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Rating and Valuation Department</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 香港住宅價格錄得四年來首次年度成長，這是迄今為止香港住宅市場開始從長期低迷中復甦的最明確信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據差餉物業估價署周三公佈的數據，2025年，香港私人住宅售價指數同比上漲3.25%，為2021年以來的首次年度成長。該指數12月較前月上漲0.2%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1_gzYN1BdfSgGPvuWFHPHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ae6f726228933f2eb8a4107f0360e952\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這個亞洲金融中心的房地產市場情緒有所回升，因按揭利率下降以及來自中國內地買家的需求。香港金管局去年曾三次下調其基準利率，與聯儲會的步調一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美聯物業數據顯示，去年，來自內地的投資者在香港購買住宅物業的金額達到了1380億港元（177億美元）的紀錄新高，約占交易總額的五分之一。在豪宅領域，受股市反彈所提振，開發商近月已完成多宗近年來最大規模的交易。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e56808cb-1733-3e77-a64a-d766387581b1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據仲量聯行表示，去年下半年房地產市場實現軟著陸，未售庫存下降。彭博行業研究預計，受創紀錄租金水平和較低利率所推動，2026年房價有望成長5%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「香港的房地產市場可能已經走到了隧道的盡頭，」Natixis亞太首席經濟學家Alicia Garcia Herrero指出，「我們仍然看到人口流入，並預計今年將進一步降息。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hong Kong Home Prices Rose for First Time in Four Years in 2025</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF2025%E5%B9%B4%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%8C%84%E5%BE%97%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-034029082.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 12:28:05",
